txt.en: Dulglok is at Shrak Mauruk.\n\nYou should bring the Crawler carcasses to Dulglok.
'I'm hungry! Get some Crawler meat and we can all have a little snack!\n\n'Hurry up, I can't wait all day to eat! I've got a war to fight here!'
Bring the Crawler carcasses to Dulglok at Shrak Mauruk
Dulglok commands you to gather some delicious crawler meat to feed the army within Osgiliath.
'Delicious! Let's all have a snack! Then back to fighting and dying you maggots!'
Crawlers can be found in Osgiliath.\n\nYou should collect Crawler carcasses.
